ygData.msgSnippet: Hmm, are you sure it was Varsoon the Undying and not just Varsoon?  I ve only seen VtU once, he was blue to me and I was definately 35 at the time. I know
ygData.messageBody:
Hmm, are you sure it was Varsoon the Undying and not just Varsoon? I've
only seen VtU once, he was blue to me and I was definately 35 at the time.
I know cause I had just trained disarm (which rangers don't get till 35) and
I was practicing it on skeletons outside Surefall. I had all my int gear on
instead of normal combat gear and all my buffs had worn off, since I really
didn't need them against the skels. When I went to check out Varsoon the
Undying, he spanked my ass good, let me tell ya. I'm guessing you saw plain
old Varsoon who was yellow to you at 20. I've never seen him in his normal
form.

Telon on E'ci
